      <details class="usage">
        <summary>Use these in your project</summary>
        <div class="usage-body">
          <p>1. Save the panels as <code>src/client.ts</code> and <code>src/types.ts</code> in your project, plus the generated <code>README.md</code> in your repo root.</p>
          <p>2. Import and use:</p>
          <pre>import {'{'} Client {'}'} from "./client";

const client = new Client({'{'} apiKey: process.env.API_KEY! {'}'});
const user = await client.users.get(42);</pre>
          <p>The generated SDK uses global <code>fetch</code> (no extra deps). Bearer / X-API-Key auth is detected automatically from your HAR.</p>
          <p>Secret values (Bearer tokens, JWTs, AWS keys, Stripe keys) are scrubbed from your input <strong>in the browser</strong> before upload — header NAMES are kept so the LLM can still infer auth shape.</p>
        </div>
